  <summary date="2021-01-11T17:11:47Z" status="Introduced in House">Care for the Veteran Caregiver Act

This bill modifies the Program of Comprehensive Assistance for Family Caregivers of the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA), including by requiring the VA to continue to provide assistance to a family caregiver for at least six months after the death of a veteran participating in the program.</summary>
